text: David McKay (born 1 March 1960 in Winnipeg) is a Canadian former wrestler who competed in the 1984 Summer Olympics and in the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Winnipeg Category:Olympic wrestlers of Canada Category:Wrestlers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Canadian male sport wrestlers Category:Commonwealth Games gold medallists for Canada Category:Wrestlers at the 1986 Commonwealth Games Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in wrestling
title: David McKay (wrestler)
